item.description:
Hi guys,

An event called Warrior Dash is happening in New England and i thought this might be a fun, sporty, outdoor thing for us girls to do!

If you've never heard of it, it's pretty much like a 5k, obstacle course race. You're going to be jumping over walls, walking tightropes, running through some mud... all that fun stuff but just a lot grimier!

Check it out:
http://warriordash.com/index.php
http://warriordash.com/register2012_new_england.php

If anyone is interested, let me know. Maybe we can carpool!!
item.name: Outdoor Event - Warrior Dash
